OL,4,CMore pupils sent home as Covid
OL,5,Cdisruption soars
OL,6, There has been a sharp rise in pupils
OL,7, sent home from school in England
OL,8, because of Covid, according to the
OL,9, latest official figures.
OL,11,FThey showed that more than 375,000
OL,12,Fpupils - about one in 20 - were out of
OL,13,Fschool for Covid-related reasons, up by
OL,14,Fmore than 130,000 in a week.
OL,16,FAbsences have quadrupled during June.
OL,18,FThe government has signalled a shift to
OL,19,Fmore Covid testing for schools in
OL,20,FSeptember - rather than having to send
OL,21,Fhome whole "bubbles" of pupils.
